28:25.862 --> 28:27.385
idea? Really? Because I've read that in 
documents, the one-third, two-thirds. You have?

28:34.077 --> 28:35.620
Yeah. I read that in histories and I didn't know 
that was your basic idea. I thought that they would

28:41.602 --> 28:44.566
have proposed that, because they didn't. Oh, 
should have left it to them. They would say, well,

28:46.028 --> 28:47.910
you pay for the whole thing. We'll just 
participate.

28:51.274 --> 29:04.430
