41:08.180 --> 41:18.954
taking advantage of what were legal rights of 
people going to other nations and all, and I didn't

41:08.180 --> 41:18.954
blame Canada for this. Okay. Now, let's leave and 
talk about the Air Work Comp. What was the Air War

41:27.710 --> 41:30.913
College Institute?

