politics to economics to psychological, to

43:53.375 --> 44:22.757
actual military problems and principles, the 
principles of war, how the growing, and

43:53.375 --> 44:22.757
particularly taken from the lesson of World War 
II, how nations depend on one another, combined

43:53.375 --> 44:22.757
planning, joint planning, alliances, and then 
right on down to tactics and technique of

43:53.375 --> 44:22.757
operating the advanced equipment the problems of 
training. It covered the waterfront, just about.

